        "bullets": [
            "Yemen's armed forces declared a full naval blockade against Saudi Arabia, citing a 'blockade for blockade' principle, per Iranian state media IRNA (not independently confirmed).",
            "Crisis Pressure holds in the extreme band while the 30-day Escalation Forecast has risen into the elevated band, with Polymarket closure odds now the top forecast driver.",
